This topic explains how to install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP manually.

## <a id="overview"></a> Overview

You can install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP with either the <%= vars.app_runtime_full %> (<%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>) or <%= vars.k8s_runtime_full %> (<%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>) runtime.

To install <%= vars.platform_name %> on GCP manually, do one of the following:

* Install with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>. See [Install Manually with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>](#manual-pas).
* Install with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>. See [Install Manually with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>](#manual-pks).

## <a id="manual-pas"></a> Install Manually with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>

To install manually with <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>, do the following:

1. Prepare to deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. See [Preparing to Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/prepare-env-manual.html).

1. Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. See [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/config-manual.html).

1. (Optional). Configure a shared VPC. See [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](./gcp-shared-vpc.html).

1. Configure <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>. See [Configuring <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>](./configure-pas.html).

## <a id="manual-pks"></a> Install Manually with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>

To install manually with <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>, do the following:

1. Prepare to deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. See [Preparing to Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/prepare-env-manual.html).

1. Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. See [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on GCP Manually](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/gcp/config-manual.html).

1. (Optional). Configure a shared VPC. See [(Optional) Configuring a Shared VPC on GCP](./gcp-shared-vpc.html).

1. Configure <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %>. See [Installing <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> on GCP](https://docs.pivotal.io/pks/installing-pks-gcp.html).
